  "id": "RAW_c80fe81c",
  "title": "Gemini 现已登陆 Android Auto：5 个值得尝试的功能",
  "url": "https://blog.google/products/android/android-auto-gemini-tips/",
  "date": "2025-11-20 17:59:56",
  "author": "Guemmy Kim",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-11-20T17:59:56.457759+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"ezime\" class=\"drop-cap\">Available in over 250 million cars on the road, Android Auto is focused on making your time behind the wheel as safe, helpful and fun as possible. Now, Gemini is starting to roll out over the coming months to Android Auto users who have <a href=\"https://gemini.google/us/assistant/?hl=en\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">upgraded from Google Assistant</a> to Gemini on their phones. Gemini will continue to provide the hands-free features you rely on, but goes way further as a truly conversational AI assistant. This means instead of having to remember the exact phrase to say what you want, with Gemini you can just speak naturally, have a back and forth conversation and get more complex tasks done.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"fmdko\">Here are five things you can try:</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ezime\">1. Add stops like a local expert.</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7g4hm\"><a href=\"https://blog.google/products/maps/gemini-navigation-features-landmark-lens/\">Google Maps</a> is getting a powerful boost with Gemini, and those improvements are coming to Android Auto, too. Gemini can give you insights from reviews and answer common questions about businesses so you can discover and navigate to the hidden gems near you.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"b78v5\"><b>Add the perfect stop:</b> \"Hey Google, I need your help. I'm suddenly craving barbecue. Any good spots along my route that are open now, near my destination?\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"334rv\"><b>Get the inside scoop:</b> If a spot looks promising, continue the conversation by asking about its most popular dishes, whether the place is dog-friendly or even if its barbecue ribs get great reviews.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a split view. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for barbecue spots with easy parking. On the right, a Google Maps interface lists three restaurant options—Bubba's BBQ, The Sauce Spot, and Back Porch—next to a music player widget.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a split view. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for barbecue spots with easy parking. On the right, a Google Maps interface lists three restaurant options—Bubba's BBQ, The Sauce Spot, and Back Porch—next to a music player widget.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_1.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_1.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_1.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ezime\">2. Send and edit messages with ease.</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"j69d\">With Gemini, you don't have to dictate your text messages perfectly, start over because you forgot to add a crucial detail, or manually add your ETA. Plus, when a bunch of messages come in while you are driving, Gemini can summarize them and help you reply with confidence.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ci6eb\"><b>Share your ETA with the perfect emoji:</b> \"Oops, I'm stuck in traffic. Can you let Leo know and add my ETA and a sorry emoji?\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"3aa49\"><b>Adjust without starting over and translate into over 40 languages:</b> \"One more thing. Can you also ask if he wants to grab coffee after the game? And please translate the message into Spanish.\"</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a messaging interaction. On the left, a voice command transcription asks to text Leo about being stuck in traffic. On the right, a notification card shows an incoming message from Leo asking &quot;What's your status?&quot; alongside a map navigation view.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a messaging interaction. On the left, a voice command transcription asks to text Leo about being stuck in traffic. On the right, a notification card shows an incoming message from Leo asking &quot;What's your status?&quot; alongside a map navigation view.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_2.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_2.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_2.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ezime\">3. Stay productive on your drive with Gmail and more.</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"ap865\">Turn your commute from \"drive time\" into \"done time.\" With Gemini, you can now access your emails in Gmail while driving.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"90fjj\"><b>Find info buried in your email:</b> \"Okay, I have a hotel booked for tonight. I think the address is in my email. Can you check and navigate there?\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"71g1f\"><b>Catch up on your inbox:</b> Ask for a summary of your unread emails to stay on top of things.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"25l5p\">And of course, Gemini still helps you check your calendar, capture to-dos and take notes — now in a much more conversational way. Google Calendar, Google Tasks, Google Keep, Samsung Calendar, Samsung Reminder and Samsung Notes are supported today, with more third party apps coming over time.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An Android Auto screen displaying Gemini connecting to Google Workspace. On the left, a voice command transcription asks to find a hotel address in an email. On the right, a Google Maps navigation view sits next to a media player widget playing &quot;Sound of Spring&quot;.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"An Android Auto screen displaying Gemini connecting to Google Workspace. On the left, a voice command transcription asks to find a hotel address in an email. On the right, a Google Maps navigation view sits next to a media player widget playing &quot;Sound of Spring&quot;.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_3_Amtk1dL.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_3_Amtk1dL.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_3_Amtk1dL.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ezime\">4. Create the perfect vibe on the fly.</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"eq2a1\">Getting the right soundtrack for your drive is now as simple as asking for it. You don't need to remember a specific song name or genre to enjoy media on YouTube Music, Spotify and more.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"9ajc1\"><b>Get a playlist for any occasion:</b> \"Can you give me a road trip playlist? Ideally something upbeat, about 3 hours long, that's good for both me and the kids.\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"3uv8\"><b>Let your imagination be the guide:</b> Be creative and have fun with it, asking for music that fits your mood or the weather. \"It's raining. Can you play songs perfect for a rainy drive?\"</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a music request. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for an upbeat road trip playlist for kids. On the right, a media player card shows a track titled &quot;You got to listen&quot; overlaid on a map navigation screen\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"An Android Auto screen displaying a music request. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for an upbeat road trip playlist for kids. On the right, a media player card shows a track titled &quot;You got to listen&quot; overlaid on a map navigation screen\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_4.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_4.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_4.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"ezime\">5. Learn, brainstorm and rehearse while you drive.</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"67pg9\">You'll be able to go Live with Gemini in beta to chat through anything on your mind. When you say \"Hey Google, let's talk live,\" Gemini can help you learn something new, brainstorm ideas, rehearse for important moments and much more, all in one continuous conversation.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"6lqma\"><b>Learn about your destination:</b> \"Alright, I'm driving to St. Louis for a wedding. Can you be my tour guide and share some fun facts about it?...\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"283m4\"><b>Brainstorm gift ideas:</b> \"...Thanks for teaching me all about St. Louis. Changing topics, The rehearsal dinner is at his parents house, and I'd like to get them a small something. What are some good ideas…\"</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"5ouha\"><b>Rehearse so you can walk in feeling confident</b>: \"...Great, glad we got the gift settled. I am giving a wedding speech on Saturday. Let's practice...\"</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"An Android Auto screen displaying the Gemini Live interface. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for fun facts about St. Louis. On the right, a glowing Gemini Live card with active conversation controls is shown over a Google Maps navigation route.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"An Android Auto screen displaying the Gemini Live interface. On the left, a voice command transcription asks for fun facts about St. Louis. On the right, a glowing Gemini Live card with active conversation controls is shown over a Google Maps navigation route.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_5.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_5.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Blog_5.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?lit$484738601$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini is here for Android Auto: 5 things to try&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"ezime\">The new Gemini AI assistant begins rolling out on Android Auto globally today, in 45 languages. Getting started is easy: just make sure you are using the Gemini app on your phone, and you'll see a tooltip on your car display once it's available for you. Then to use it, just say “Hey Google,” press the mic button on your car screen or long press the voice control button on your steering wheel.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"a9d3t\">This is just the beginning of our journey, and we'll be adding more capabilities over time. We can't wait to see how you use it to make every drive more helpful and fun.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gemini 正在向 Android Auto 推出，提供更具对话性的 AI 助手，以增强导航、消息功能、生产力、媒体控制和实时互动对话体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gemini 正在向 Android Auto 推出，提供更具对话性的 AI 助手，以增强导航、消息功能、生产力、媒体控制和实时互动对话体验。",
  "summary": "本文宣布 Google 的对话式 AI 助手 Gemini 现已集成到 Android Auto 中。该系统已在超过 2.5 亿辆汽车中使用。此次更新旨在通过提供免提、自然语言交互，使驾驶更安全、更有帮助和更愉快。已在其手机上升级到 Gemini 的用户将逐步收到此功能。文章重点介绍了五个关键功能：通过 Google 地图增强导航功能，允许用户查找并获取沿途站点的见解；通过编辑、翻译和消息总结等功能简化消息处理；通过与 Gmail、Google 日历和其他笔记应用程序集成来提高生产力，从而访问电子邮件和管理任务；动态媒体控制，方便在 YouTube Music 和 Spotify 等平台上创建个性化播放列表；以及用于持续对话学习、头脑风暴和排练的“Live with Gemini”测试版功能。该版本面向全球发布，支持 45 种语言。用户可以通过语音指令或汽车控制轻松激活该功能，未来还将推出更多功能。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Gemini 通过对话式 AI 增强车载导航和本地信息探索。",
      "explanation": "用户可以自然地要求 Gemini 查找并获取有关沿途兴趣点的详细信息，利用 Google 地图的见解来获得更明智和便捷的旅行体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该集成简化了通讯和工作效率，实现了消息和电子邮件的免提管理。",
      "explanation": "Gemini 允许轻松发送、编辑和总结消息，以及访问和管理电子邮件和日历事件，从而将通勤时间转化为高效时间。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 在 Android Auto 中提供动态媒体控制和互动学习体验。",
      "explanation": "用户可以根据心情或场合生成自定义播放列表，并进行持续对话以进行学习、头脑风暴或排练，从而使驾驶体验更加个性化和引人入胜。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Gemini 将继续提供您依赖的免提功能，但作为真正的对话式 AI 助手，它的功能远不止于此。",
    "有了 Gemini，您无需再完美地口述短信，也不用因为忘记添加关键信息而重新开始，更不必手动添加预计到达时间。",
    "将您的通勤从“驾驶时间”变成“完成时间”。借助 Gemini，您现在可以在驾驶时访问 Gmail 中的电子邮件。",
    "现在，只需简单提问，就能获得适合您驾驶的完美配乐。",
    "当您说“Hey Google， let's talk live，”时，Gemini 就能在一个持续的对话中，帮助您学习新知识、集思广益、为重要时刻进行排练等等。"
  ],
